
Single java class to compute the size and position of the secondary mirror of a Newton telescope.

See docs/index.html (in French) to understand the meaning of variables.

Usage: 
- Adapt the values of variables f, D, fpp, d, h in method main()
- run: java SecondaryMirror.java

Repository created on 2024-02-23 by Thierry Graff

Originally published on https://tig12.net/astronomy/position-miroir-secondaire/position-miroir-secondaire.html
